comment: Duncan (SAS) sets the screen on Harden (HOU) without giving him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction as he extends his hip to make contact.
Duncan (SAS) cleanly knocks the ball away from Howard (HOU).
Howard (HOU) impedes Duncan (SAS) as he cuts away from the ball.
Diaw (SAS) remains in legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket and layup attempt by Harden (HOU).
Harden (HOU) makes body to body contact that affects Ginobili's (SAS) RSBQ as he drives toward the basket.
Harden (HOU) cleanly knocks the ball away from Ginobili (SAS).

Duncan (SAS) jumps vertically on Harden's (HOU) layup attempt and cleanly blocks the shot. There is contact after the blocked shot, but because the shot is already blocked, the contact is incidental and deemed to have no impact on the shot attempt.
